  "_comment": "3x3 matrix configuration. Each entry under <attr>.clips becomes one panel rendered by panel.html. The `features` list is ordered: the first feature is the *strongest correlated* one (shown at the top, drives the highlight sphere on the robot, and is the one synthetically exaggerated on the high side's robot). Features use the G1 joint names from g1_engine/model/g1_model.json. `source_bvh` is the path under bones-seed used by generate_smpl_matrix.py. To add/remove panels, edit this file and reload matrix.html.",

